<p style="text-align:start"><strong>Colonial Skilled Nursing Home &amp; Rehabilitation &bull; </strong>Located in Weymouth, Massachusetts, Colonial Rehabilitation &amp; Nursing Center is a 173-bed skilled nursing facility offering sub-acute,&nbsp;<a href="/baneCare/Colonial-skilled-programs-services#shortRehab" style="outline: none; color: rgb(17, 113, 169); text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">short-term rehabilitation</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;long-term care. Distinctive services provided at Colonial include the Richard M. Welch Sub-Acute Unit for individuals with more complicated diagnoses and the&nbsp;<a href="/baneCare/Colonial-skilled-programs-services#pulm" style="outline: none; color: rgb(17, 113, 169); text-decoration: none;">Pulmonary Care Program</a>&nbsp;providing comprehensive short-term pulmonary care services.</p>  <p style="text-align:start"><br /> Colonial&rsquo;s skilled medical staff is committed to providing the highest quality&nbsp;<a href="http://www.welchhrg.com/senior-living-resources/skilled-nursing-faq" style="outline: none; color: rgb(17, 113, 169); text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">skilled nursing</a>&nbsp;and short-term rehabilitative care. Our mandate is for each resident to achieve the best quality of life while maintaining or regaining function, health and well-being.</p>  <p style="text-align:start"><br /> To ensure residents feel at home, Colonial offers private and semi-private rooms and amenities such as a library, pub, private sitting and living rooms, musical entertainment and a range of activities. Each resident has immediate access to cable TV and private telephone service. Residents enjoy meals in our elegant dining room or in their own room, depending upon individual preference.</p>  <p style="text-align:start"><br /> Colonial is accredited by&nbsp;<a href="http://www.jointcommission.org/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(17, 113, 169); text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">The Joint Commission</a>&nbsp;and is Medicare/Medicaid Certified as well as accepts coverage from many private insurers. We are conveniently located a short distance from Route 3 and Route 53.</p>  <ul style="list-style-type:disc; margin-left:40px"> 	<li><a href="http://www.welchhrg.com/_pdfs/WelchRehabNursing.brochure2015Update_v4_FINAL.pdf" style="outline: none; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(17, 113, 169);" target="_blank">Click here for our Rehabilitation Brochure</a></li> </ul> 